@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    At Student Registration, we value your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our website or use our services. By using our platform, you agree to the practices described below.
</p>

<!-- 1. Data Collection -->
<h2>1. Data Collection</h2>
<p>We collect personal information when you use our website and services. This may include:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Personal identification information (e.g., name, email address, phone number)</li>
    <li>Login credentials (e.g., username, password)</li>
    <li>Demographic information (e.g., age, gender, location)</li>
    <li>Usage data (e.g., pages visited, features used, interaction logs)</li>
</ul>

<!-- 2. How We Use Your Data -->
<h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
<p>We use the data we collect for the following purposes:</p>
<ul>
    <li>To provide, maintain, and improve our services</li>
    <li>To personalize the user experience</li>
    <li>To process transactions and manage user accounts</li>
    <li>To send service updates, newsletters, or relevant communications</li>
    <li>To comply with legal requirements and protect the security of our platform</li>
</ul>

<!-- 3. Data Storage and Protection -->
<h2>3. Data Storage and Protection</h2>
<p>
    We implement various security measures to protect your personal information. Data is stored on secure servers, and sensitive data is transmitted using encryption protocols (e.g., SSL). While we strive to safeguard your information, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure.
</p>

<!-- 4. Cookies and Tracking Technologies -->
<h2>4. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
<p>
    We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience. Cookies are small data files stored on your device. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but doing so may limit certain functionalities on our website.
</p>

<!-- 5. Data Sharing and Disclosure -->
<h2>5. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
<p>
    We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information. However, we may share your data under the following circumstances:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>With trusted service providers assisting with website operations</li>
    <li>To comply with legal obligations or enforce our policies</li>
    <li>During a merger, acquisition, or transfer of ownership</li>
</ul>

<!-- 6. User Rights -->
<h2>6. User Rights</h2>
<p>You have the following rights regarding your personal information:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Right to access your personal data</li>
    <li>Right to correct or update your personal data</li>
    <li>Right to delete your personal data (subject to legal requirements)</li>
    <li>Right to withdraw consent for data processing (if applicable)</li>
    <li>Right to object to how we process your data</li>
</ul>
<p>
    To exercise any of these rights, contact us at: <strong>support@studentregistration.com</strong>.
</p>

<!-- 7. Data Retention -->
<h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
<p>
    We retain your personal data only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy or as required by law.
</p>

<!-- 8. Changes to This Privacy Policy -->
<h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page, and the "Last Updated" date will be modified accordingly. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
</p>

